Path: This week in Nu #47
Content:
arashout began work to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2139] auto generate documentation
, fixed issues 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2164] (2164)
.
k-brk moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2197] ``keep``
 suite
 unifying 
``keep-while``
 and 
``keep-until``
fdncred added 
``--dark_bg``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2189] change color and text backgrounds
 of the html, added internal 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2157/files] assertion improvement
, added 
``--html_color``
 and 
``--no_color``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2158] for finer grained color control
 in html.
jonathandturner 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2199] introduced wasm support
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2165] extended Shell
 to support 
``open``
 and 
``save``
, introduced 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2186] configurable keybindings
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2150] clearer printing
 of duration, split 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2151] ``config set``
 arguments
, renamed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2153] byte primitive
 for clarity, and fixed issues 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2152] 2152
Porges fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2181] row indices formatting
 alignment
andrasio added support for 
``group-by``
 to pass a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2172] block as the key function
. moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2179] ``skip``
 suite
 unifying 
``skip-while``
 and 
``skip-until``
, made 
``str``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2173] stricter
.
JosephTLyons added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2170] ``reverse``
 subcommand
 to 
``str``
, did improvements in the code 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2176] 2176
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2177] 2177
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2183] 2183
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2184] 2184
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2194] 2194
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2196] 2196
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2201] 2201
amousa introduced 
``variance``
 and 
``stddev``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2154] subcommands to 
``math``
.
thegedge introduced 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2198] completion abstractions
, fixed an issue 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2168] with the encoder
 for preventing overflows of data.
samhedin documented 
``auto-env``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2163] more
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2148] more tests
. Fixes preventing env script 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2171] running multiple times
.
bailey-layzer added 
``from``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2125] subcommand to 
``str``
, and 
``--char``
 flag for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2162] trimmin specific ones
.
ritobanrc updated 
``config``
 command suite 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2146] flags to subcommands
.
pag4k added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2128] ns seconds
 to Duration
